charges.charge_description: 21:841(a)(1) and 841(b)(1)(B) - Possession with Intent to Distribute Methamphetamine(2s)

charges.charge_disposition: The defendant is committed to the custody of the Bureau of Prisons for a term of THIRTY-THREE (33) MONTHS, with credit for time served. Upon release from imprisonment, the defendant shall be placed on supervised release for a term of SIXTY (60) MONTHS. Special Assessment $100.
